{
  "texts": [
    "Essential for evaluating the equitable distribution of model benefits and detecting demographic disparities.",
    "Bias Amplification Assesses whether the model amplifies biases present in its training data.",
    "Crucial for understanding the model's impact on existing societal biases and its ability to mitigate them.",
    "Expert Reviews Involves subjective assessment by experts of the model's outputs for biases.",
    "Provides a sophisticated understanding of bias and fairness that quantitative metrics may overlook."
  ]
}